ue, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["私に", "負けたけど。"]}, {"box": [407, 103, 455, 200], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ぐっ．．．", "しまった．．"]}, {"box": [339, 111, 363, 214], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["次は勝つし．．．"]}, {"box": [153, 121, 173, 187], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あはは。"]}, {"box": [94, 160, 123, 287], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["期待してるよ。"]}, {"box": [674, 498, 752, 617], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["それで", "どこまで", "走ってるの？"]}, {"box": [377, 472, 430, 609], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いやー、割りと", "テキトーかなー。"]}, {"box": [98, 485, 149, 646], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["疲れたら", "帰るってカンジで。"]}, {"box": [698, 759, 753, 855], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["前は海まで", "行ったよ。"]}, {"box": [384, 786, 416, 835], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["海！？"]}, {"box": [264, 767, 296, 844], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["へぇー。"]}], "img_path": "122.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [727, 58, 753, 110], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["おお。"]}, {"box": [619, 63, 694, 216], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["めずらしく", "高木さんがオレに", "感心している。"]}, {"box": [349, 99, 369, 176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["これは．．"]}, {"box": [254, 100, 277, 195], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ホントに？"]}, {"box": [94, 113, 144, 192], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ホント", "だって！！"]}, {"box": [658, 525, 715, 671], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["結構", "距離あるしなー。"]}, {"box": [584, 546, 604, 665], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ホントかなー。"]}, {"box": [371, 717, 406, 735], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["西片"]}, {"box": [146, 539, 196, 672], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ホントだって！！", "絶対に！！"]}, {"box": [678, 908, 725, 1026], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ま、じゃあ", "頑張ってねー。"]}, {"box": [332, 894, 394, 1006], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["絶対", "信じてない"]}], "img_path": "123.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [697, 79, 773, 204], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["よし！", "今から", "海まで行って、"]}, {"box": [179, 101, 233, 235], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["証拠写真を", "迷ってやろう！！"]}, {"box": [443, 335, 516, 394], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["２", "西片"]}, {"box": [688, 624, 734, 728], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["くくく", "高木さんめ"]}, {"box": [118, 632, 194, 728], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["すごいって", "言わせて", "やるぞ。"]}], "img_path": "124.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [534, 61, 559, 157], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["キツイ．．．"]}, {"box": [123, 560, 151, 637], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["体力が．．．"]}, {"box": [616, 551, 749, 686], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さんに", "会った時点で", "そろそろ", "帰ろうと", "思ってたから．．．"]}, {"box": [340, 817, 362, 933], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["やめるか．．．？"]}, {"box": [98, 817, 119, 882], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}], "img_path": "125.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [787, 83, 816, 157], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["いや！"]}, {"box": [725, 123, 749, 261], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["頑張れオレ！！"]}, {"box": [636, 100, 659, 247], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["海まで行けば、"]}, {"box": [221, 18, 408, 114], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["えすごい両片！！", "もうからかわない！！"]}, {"box": [148, 110, 173, 281], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ってなるんだぞ。"]}, {"box": [390, 431, 414, 500], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["フフッ。"]}, {"box": [658, 779, 680, 903], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["はっはッはー。"]}, {"box": [164, 807, 217, 892], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["見てろよ", "高木さん"]}], "img_path": "126.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [82, 52, 371, 72], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [694, 366, 715, 437], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ついた．．．"]}, {"box": [619, 841, 649, 905], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ふー．．．"]}, {"box": [466, 847, 520, 926], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["達成感が", "すごい．．．"]}, {"box": [304, 832, 407, 1006], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["いや、それどころ", "じゃない", "さっさと高木さんに", "写真を。"]}], "img_path": "127.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [782, 45, 809, 99], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["よし、"]}, {"box": [617, 56, 644, 142], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["送信っと。"]}, {"box": [447, 50, 554, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["くくく．．．", "高木さんめ、", "思い知るが", "いいの"]}, {"box": [492, 582, 633, 669], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["夕日きれいだね。", "ありがと"]}, {"box": [684, 885, 733, 1038], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いや！？", "そこじゃなくて！！"]}, {"box": [253, 890, 284, 960], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["海だよ。"]}, {"box": [103, 892, 205, 1047], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["これじゃあオレ、", "夕日を高木さんに", "送っただけのやつ", "じゃん！"]}], "img_path": "128.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [698, 73, 726, 151], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["違うの？"]}, {"box": [708, 607, 740, 721], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["高木さん！？"]}, {"box": [338, 603, 385, 764], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あはは、", "いい反応するなー。"]}, {"box": [433, 717, 460, 868], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["なんでここに。"]}, {"box": [607, 977, 697, 1125], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["おつかい", "終わってから", "自転車とはした", "かいがあったよー。"]}, {"box": [161, 971, 183, 1040], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．！"]}], "img_path": "129.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [748, 59, 793, 149], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あ．．．", "ありがと．．．"]}, {"box": [386, 70, 491, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["証拠撮ろうとして", "海まで行くん", "だろうなって", "思ってたら、"]}, {"box": [100, 243, 154, 330], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["その通り", "だったよ。"]}, {"box": [729, 539, 747, 566], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["！？"]}, {"box": [626, 501, 671, 597], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["オレはまた", "まんまと．．．"]}, {"box": [414, 510, 435, 572], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ぐう．．．"]}, {"box": [107, 505, 159, 631], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["でも、", "うれしいなぁ。"]}, {"box": [660, 892, 738, 1001], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["西片が私に", "夕日の写真", "送るために、"]}, {"box": [528, 881, 605, 1017], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["頑張って", "走ってくれたん", "だもんねー。"]}, {"box": [117, 912, 153, 967], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["な！？"]}], "img_path": "130.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [692, 66, 740, 182], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "そうだけど．．"]}, {"box": [487, 165, 505, 318], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["そうじゃなくて．．．"]}, {"box": [200, 134, 230, 246], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["真っ赤だね。"]}, {"box": [43, 73, 102, 173], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["違．．．"]}, {"box": [650, 549, 687, 608], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["夕日。"]}, {"box": [725, 855, 750, 902], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [246, 856, 263, 943], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["なんでも．．．"]}], "img_path": "131.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [728, 105, 807, 206], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["まぁ", "西片の方が", "赤いけど。"]}, {"box": [388, 116, 488, 251], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．", "すごいと", "思わせたかった", "だけなのに。"]}, {"box": [631, 465, 732, 600], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["はー、ホントに", "西片追いかけて", "きたかいか", "あったよ。"]}, {"box": [111, 244, 157, 367], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["そのために", "頑張ったのに"]}, {"box": [183, 500, 201, 564], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [397, 765, 455, 919], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["西片と", "夕日見れたしね。"]}, {"box": [121, 703, 156, 742], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["へ。"]}], "img_path": "132.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [349, 147, 401, 217], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["きれい", "だねー。"]}, {"box": [335, 699, 378, 787], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["いやいや！！", "ウソだ！！"]}, {"box": [261, 693, 301, 813], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["からかいに来た", "だけだろ。"]}, {"box": [103, 716, 120, 828], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["だまされるか。"]}, {"box": [258, 1007, 374, 1114], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["くそ．．．いっちゃ", "一瞬でも", "ドキっとした", "オレが", "バカだった．．．"]}], "img_path": "133.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [583, 56, 660, 173], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["それにしても", "すごいね", "西片。"]}, {"box": [330, 123, 405, 228], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ホントに", "海まで", "走るなんて。"]}, {"box": [523, 394, 556, 413], "vertical": false, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["西片"]}, {"box": [316, 656, 369, 726], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["．．．いや、", "別に．．．"]}, {"box": [643, 922, 721, 1027], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あ、西片", "ほめられて", "ニヤけてる。"]}, {"box": [345, 942, 395, 1039], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ニヤけて", "ないって！"]}, {"box": [129, 922, 235, 1058], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["目的は", "達成したけど", "全然勝った気が", "しなかった。"]}], "img_path": "134.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "135.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [675, 124, 730, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["突然だけど", "高木さん。"]}, {"box": [222, 132, 267, 229], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["グリコって", "知ってる？"]}, {"box": [646, 576, 696, 672], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["じゃんけん", "の？"]}, {"box": [536, 588, 558, 637], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そう。"]}, {"box": [432, 576, 486, 678], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["何を出して", "勝ったかで、"]}, {"box": [279, 558, 377, 719], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["んっ．．．"]}, {"box": [98, 589, 172, 704], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["それぞれ", "何歩進めるか", "決まるやつ。"]}, {"box": [422, 908, 475, 1011], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["それで勝負", "しないかい。"]}, {"box": [99, 900, 121, 983], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いいけど。"]}], "img_path": "136.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [670, 134, 743, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "神社の", "鳥居まで。"]}, {"box": [383, 141, 404, 227], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["オッケー。"]}, {"box": [290, 113, 319, 230], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["でも大丈夫？"]}, {"box": [80, 51, 372, 72], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [105, 119, 158, 273], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["西片、じゃんけん", "弱いのに。"]}, {"box": [102, 347, 137, 434], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["くすくす"]}, {"box": [693, 535, 748, 670], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんか作戦でも", "あるのかなー。"]}, {"box": [98, 558, 176, 657], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ふっ．．．", "その通りさ", "高木さん"]}, {"box": [687, 929, 712, 1006], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["オレは、"]}, {"box": [128, 941, 183, 1055], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["チョキしか", "出さん！！"]}], "img_path": "137.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [673, 108, 754, 269], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["もし高木さんが", "勝つとすれば", "歩数の少ないグー。"]}, {"box": [132, 118, 212, 273], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["負けてもオレに", "大したダメージは", "ない。"]}, {"box": [667, 505, 753, 643], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["高木さん３歩に", "対してオレは", "６歩。"]}, {"box": [366, 532, 419, 684], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["３回に１回勝てば", "トントンなのさ。"]}, {"box": [91, 670, 124, 711], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["けー"]}, {"box": [287, 880, 309, 923], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}], "img_path": "138.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [388, 53, 489, 213], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そしてそろそろ", "気付いたようだな、", "オレがチョキしか", "出さないと．．．"]}, {"box": [282, 45, 357, 171], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["そう．．．", "グーをっ", "出し続ければ、"]}, {"box": [87, 284, 141, 405], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さんは", "勝てるのだよ。"]}, {"box": [103, 592, 169, 742], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["出し続け", "られれば．．．ね。"]}, {"box": [657, 905, 733, 1109], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["もしオレが気まぐれで", "パーを出したらという", "疑惑．．．"]}, {"box": [552, 912, 600, 1052], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["それは精神を", "すり減らすハズ。"]}, {"box": [92, 912, 167, 1067], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["そう、これは", "オレとの勝負じゃ", "ないのさ。"]}], "img_path": "139.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [557, 66, 612, 172], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["自分と", "戦うがいい"]}, {"box": [370, 136, 398, 221], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["高木さん"]}, {"box": [302, 125, 323, 185], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ふーん。"]}], "img_path": "140.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [700, 108, 748, 212], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ふふふ．．．", "作戦成功だ。"]}, {"box": [373, 108, 425, 229], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["あと１回で", "オレの勝ちだ。"]}, {"box": [208, 100, 241, 147], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ポン"]}, {"box": [138, 544, 186, 632], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ああ．．．", "そうだね。"]}, {"box": [686, 536, 736, 692], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どっちが勝っても", "これで決着だね。"]}, {"box": [641, 851, 747, 1025], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["しかし", "ここまでホントに", "チョキしか出さない", "とはねー。"]}, {"box": [363, 854, 385, 958], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ぶっふっふ。"]}, {"box": [264, 868, 312, 982], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どうだオレの", "作戦は。"]}], "img_path": "141.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [387, 174, 460, 270], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["おかげで", "調整しやす", "かったよ。"]}, {"box": [90, 140, 118, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["な。"]}, {"box": [606, 469, 735, 625], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ふっ．．．", "負け惜しみを．．．", "調整だと．．．？", "高木さんに", "メリットがない．．．"]}, {"box": [117, 452, 166, 573], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["そう．．．", "負け惜しみさ"]}, {"box": [702, 779, 735, 836], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ねえ。"]}, {"box": [479, 782, 528, 942], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["どうせあと１回で", "勝負決まるんだし。"]}, {"box": [119, 794, 171, 928], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["罰ゲーム", "決めとかない？"]}], "img_path": "142.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [640, 124, 747, 223], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["グー出して", "負けたら", "ジュースを", "おごる。"]}, {"box": [317, 112, 395, 255], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["パーを出して", "負けたら", "デコピンされる。"]}, {"box": [234, 57, 253, 117], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["どう？"]}, {"box": [721, 512, 746, 591], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["それで．．．"]}, {"box": [42, 273, 96, 343], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["あぁ．．．", "いいよ。"]}, {"box": [419, 558, 468, 673], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["チョキで", "負けたら．．．？"]}, {"box": [404, 840, 424, 925], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["キスして。"]}], "img_path": "143.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [700, 73, 731, 119], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["へ？"]}, {"box": [556, 80, 608, 168], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "いくよー。"]}, {"box": [465, 79, 513, 158], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["じゃーん", "けーん．．．"]}, {"box": [210, 107, 227, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["え．．．！？"]}, {"box": [206, 105, 230, 166], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["え．．．！？"]}, {"box": [128, 151, 143, 206], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["ええ！？"]}, {"box": [126, 150, 144, 207], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ええ！？"]}, {"box": [667, 468, 740, 644], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["どうする．．．ここで", "チョキを出したら．．", "まるで．．"]}, {"box": [108, 480, 207, 631], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["オレがキスを", "したがっていると", "いうことに", "なるのか．．．！？"]}, {"box": [701, 782, 750, 897], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "なるワケが．．"]}, {"box": [483, 772, 556, 991], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ここまで", "チョキでつらぬいて", "きたのに今さら他のは．．．"]}, {"box": [418, 774, 438, 874], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["いやしかし"]}, {"box": [183, 800, 208, 868], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["もしも、"]}, {"box": [97, 840, 144, 937], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["チョキで", "負けたら．．．"]}, {"box": [410, 1032, 432, 1120], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["くそおぉ。"]}], "img_path": "144.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [394, 80, 425, 138], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ぽん。"]}, {"box": [716, 577, 739, 662], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あぁあぁ。"]}, {"box": [91, 588, 141, 667], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["やったー", "勝ちー。"]}], "img_path": "145.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [712, 74, 737, 199], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["惜しかったね。"]}, {"box": [407, 56, 432, 171], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今わかった．．．"]}, {"box": [89, 76, 166, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["この．．．", "いい勝負ができた", "という状況："]}, {"box": [668, 407, 733, 533], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["完全に", "遊ばれてた。"]}, {"box": [670, 747, 749, 836], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["じゃ、", "罰ゲーム", "しよっか"]}, {"box": [246, 744, 324, 860], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["パーで", "負けたから", "デコピンか．．．"]}], "img_path": "146.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [537, 68, 559, 173], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いっくよー。"]}, {"box": [691, 921, 753, 993], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["早く", "してよ。"]}, {"box": [391, 891, 429, 977], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あはは"]}, {"box": [319, 921, 340, 1007], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["はいはい。"]}], "img_path": "147.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [506, 141, 556, 186], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ちゃっ"]}, {"box": [709, 596, 742, 644], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["へ？"]}, {"box": [365, 945, 390, 990], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [101, 938, 120, 1033], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["どしたの？"]}], "img_path": "148.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [694, 79, 747, 198], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["今．．．", "おでこに．．．？"]}, {"box": [408, 104, 433, 166], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["あれ？"]}, {"box": [354, 64, 376, 124], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あれ？"]}, {"box": [75, 63, 152, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["パーで", "負けたから", "デコピン？"]}, {"box": [670, 500, 743, 614], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["え．．．と．．．", "ハーでオレか", "負けたから．．．"]}, {"box": [567, 507, 588, 604], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["テコピン．．．"]}, {"box": [77, 274, 151, 406], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["チョキで", "勝ったらキス", "するんだっけ？"]}, {"box": [117, 500, 193, 673], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["キ．．．は．．．", "チョキで負けたら．．．", "だけど．．．"]}, {"box": [695, 834, 743, 959], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あ、そっか、", "そうだよねー。"]}, {"box": [429, 835, 448, 910], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["あれー？"]}], "img_path": "149.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [743, 84, 797, 229], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["私、今ちゃんと", "デコピンした？"]}, {"box": [404, 319, 420, 364], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [131, 351, 179, 486], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["デ．．．テコピン", "だったような．．．"]}, {"box": [586, 686, 661, 790], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そっかー", "よかったー。", "合ってて。"]}, {"box": [504, 735, 552, 822], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あはは"]}, {"box": [160, 704, 235, 864], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["デコピン．．．！？", "そうだよな！", "デコピンだ今のは、"]}, {"box": [247, 1128, 598, 1148], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["しからかい上手の高木さん田・完"]}], "img_path": "150.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "151.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [397, 41, 506, 73], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おまけ"]}, {"box": [353, 144, 425, 338], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["うへえ、", "またおかあさん", "ピーマンいれてるよお。"]}, {"box": [127, 349, 177, 498], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["残すと怒られるん", "だよなあ．．．"]}], "img_path": "152.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [630, 169, 663, 217], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["へ？"]}, {"box": [351, 130, 378, 188], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["礼は？"]}, {"box": [48, 139, 121, 290], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["はあ！？", "勝手に食べといて", "何言ってんの！？"]}, {"box": [324, 391, 348, 549], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["嫌いだったんだろ。"]}, {"box": [106, 616, 127, 719], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．ありがと。"]}, {"box": [595, 867, 642, 1014], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["よく食べられるね", "苦くない？"]}, {"box": [134, 898, 162, 1021], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ああ、苦いな。"]}], "img_path": "153.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [693, 153, 747, 244], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["苦いし言いし", "青臭いし。"]}, {"box": [319, 140, 364, 271], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["はあ？", "じゃあなんで．．．"]}, {"box": [667, 485, 725, 587], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["好きだから", "．．．だな。"]}, {"box": [431, 821, 480, 888], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["はっ！", "てたよ。"]}, {"box": [145, 844, 199, 1029], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["苦いの好きとかいう", "大人っぽさアピール。"]}], "img_path": "154.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [666, 120, 735, 251], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["えー、あいつ", "ピーマンめちゃ", "嫌いだよ、確か。"]}, {"box": [574, 121, 627, 201], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["小学校同じ", "だったから", "しってるけど"]}, {"box": [385, 121, 455, 247], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["えーなにー", "じゃあ強がりな", "わけ？"]}, {"box": [490, 375, 567, 495], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["いや、", "好きな人が", "困ってたから、"]}, {"box": [377, 273, 445, 341], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["何だか"]}, {"box": [429, 438, 452, 595], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["って意味だと思う。"]}, {"box": [562, 699, 669, 878], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いや、違うって！", "強がってんだって！", "あいつそういうとこ", "あるって！！"]}, {"box": [352, 693, 373, 824], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["聞いてみたら？"]}, {"box": [138, 755, 167, 827], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["やだ！！"]}, {"box": [52, 964, 92, 1076], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おわー"]}], "img_path": "155.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [131, 93, 612, 142], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさんは"]}, {"box": [133, 180, 568, 203], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ゲッサン少年サンデーコミックススペシャル"]}, {"box": [195, 548, 499, 564], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["２０２０年３月１７日初版第１刷発行"]}, {"box": [439, 513, 759, 528], "vertical": false, "font_size": 13.5, "lines": ["０９－８５００３４－５", "ＩＳＢＮ９７８－４－Ｃ"]}, {"box": [193, 651, 262, 685], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["著", "者"]}, {"box": [197, 726, 262, 787], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["発行者", "ＥＤＦＵフィ"]}, {"box": [402, 651, 664, 751], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.333333333333332, "lines": ["山本宗一朗", "ＣＳＳｉｎｔｉｏＴｏＴａｎａｍａｎｎｏｗｓ２０１", "樹正田組"]}, {"box": [137, 823, 709, 931], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["「ゲッサン」２０１９年４月号〜７月号、９月号〟１０月号。１２月号、２０１２年１月号掲載作品", "連載担当ノ板谷真人", "単行本編集責任ノ石川昌彦", "単行本編集ノ板谷真人。〈三輪抜子（アイブロダクション）"]}, {"box": [408, 768, 618, 785], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["中央精版印刷株式会社"]}, {"box": [617, 800, 718, 812], "vertical": false, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["ＰＲＩＮＴＥＤＩＮＪ"]}, {"box": [142, 942, 240, 979], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["発行所"]}, {"box": [256, 943, 599, 962], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["〈〒１０－＊８０１）東京都千代田区一ツ橋二の三の"]}, {"box": [138, 1027, 762, 1142], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["●法本には十分注意しでおりますが、印刷、製本なと製造上の不備がございましたら「制作局コール", "センター「パフリーダイヤルＩＤＥ」３８６－６８２にご連絡ください。", "〈電話受付は、土・日・提供日を除く９，３０〜１７：８０", "●本書の一部または全部を無断で複製、転載、複写（コピー）、スキャン、デジタル化、上演、放送", "等をすることは、著作権法上での例外を除き禁じられています。代行業者等の第三者による本書の", "電子的複製も認められておりません。"]}, {"box": [425, 965, 741, 1018], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["２０１８年１１月１２日に編集のパスターマッチング", "平成２８年１０月２８日、現在は５８０１５年６月１５日に３０１３年３月２５日、東京・東京大学大学院の"]}], "img_path": "156.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [103, 761, 716, 945], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高木さん１３", "山本崇一朗", "○山本崇一朗ノ小学館", "書名著者名", "株式会社小学年", "行", "発", "〒１０１－８００１．東京都千代田区一ツ橋２・３－"]}, {"box": [121, 991, 575, 1023], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["電子書籍制作会社株式会社昭和ブライト"]}, {"box": [123, 1065, 661, 1106], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["淡収録されている作品は、執筆された当時の状況や年代を考慮の上、", "初回掲載時の表現のまま掲載されております。ご了承ください"]}], "img_path": "157.jpg"}]}